## Current story

**ID:** STORY-021
**Title:** Subject confidence trend chart (7-day history)
**Description:** ConfidenceCalibrationView saves a timestamped history of confidence readings per subject. StudyModeView shows a SwiftUI Charts line chart of the last 7 readings per subject, so Ammar can see if his confidence is trending up or down.

**Acceptance criteria:**
- PlannerStore has `confidenceHistory: [String: [ConfidenceReading]]` where ConfidenceReading has date: Date and value: Double
- Every time calibration is submitted, a new ConfidenceReading is appended (capped at 30 entries per subject)
- StudyModeView subject detail panel shows a LineChart of last 7 readings using SwiftUI Charts
- Chart x-axis shows abbreviated dates (Mon, Tue…), y-axis 0-100
- If fewer than 2 readings exist, show 'Complete calibration to see trend' placeholder
